                Philosophy
                <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-0 h-px bg-lituus-pink transition-all group-hover:w-full duration-300"></span>
            </a>
            <a href="#mechanism" class="hover:text-lituus-pink transition-colors relative group">
